Natural acceptance is process to understand ourselves first.Natural accepatance implies unconitional and total acceptance of the self, people and environment.It is a way to accept the good things naturally.In other words acceptance is human psychology is person's assent to the reality of a situation, recognizing a process or condition without attempting to changing it or protest it.It also refers to the abscence of exception from others.

We need natural acceptance because once we fully and trully commit ourselves on the basis of natural accepance, we feel a holistic sense of inner harmony, tranquility and fulfillment.It enables us to understand 'what is valueable ' for human happiness helps us to understand our needs and visualize our goals correctly and also helps to remove our confusions and contradictions and bring harmony at all levels.

We can achive natural acceptance if we dont consider the factors such as pear pressure , thinking  of others judjement , etc .
